== 余波 ==
由于风暴造成了严重灾难，其名称“乔治”因此退役，之后永远都不会再在[[北大西洋热带气旋|大西洋飓风]]命名时采用<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml#retired | title = Retired Hurricane Names Since 1954 | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 2009 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141027024120/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml#retired | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-27 | accessdate = 2014-12-14}}</ref>。用来取代的新名称是“加斯顿”（{{lang|en|Gaston}}），于[[2004年大西洋飓风季|2004年大西洋飓风季]]首度采用<ref>{{cite web | author = James L. Franklin, Daniel P. Brown and Colin McAdie | title = Hurricane Gaston Tropical Cyclone Report | year = 2004 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-12-14 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL072004_Gaston.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120925070000/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL072004_Gaston.pdf | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-09-25 }}</ref>。

